1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:01,140
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:01,210 --> 00:00:03,270
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,340 --> 00:00:05,040
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:06,710 --> 00:00:08,550
The password to the Swiss account?

5
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:10,080
If we know it,

6
00:00:10,850 --> 00:00:12,250
we could take Jin Tae Seok down
in one fell swoop.

7
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:14,520
Tell me something I don't know.

8
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:16,250
But how on earth are you going
to find it out?

9
00:00:16,650 --> 00:00:17,860
I've failed once before.

10
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:18,890
But this time...

11
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:21,560
I think I've succeeded.

12
00:00:23,290 --> 00:00:24,730
You're saying
we have it in our hands?

13
00:00:25,030 --> 00:00:26,400
Jung Won made a move.

14
00:00:27,370 --> 00:00:29,300
And Joo Ha Neul helped her.

15
00:00:30,070 --> 00:00:34,740
What? How did that happen?
Tell me, quick! I'm dying to know.

16
00:00:46,950 --> 00:00:48,090
Se Mi, what's wrong?

17
00:00:49,390 --> 00:00:51,160
I don't know what to do.

18
00:00:51,620 --> 00:00:52,920
Tell me. Take your time.

19
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:58,030
Se Hoon told me
Dad has a Swiss account,

20
00:00:58,430 --> 00:01:00,730
and he wanted me
to find out the password.

21
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,500
Ha Neul bribed the board members?

22
00:01:06,810 --> 00:01:07,840
Is that what you think?

23
00:01:09,010 --> 00:01:10,810
I know Ha Neul isn't
that kind of person.

24
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:16,850
Is your offer to help
still on the table?

25
00:01:20,390 --> 00:01:21,720
My dad is in the wrong.

26
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:25,720
And the look
in Se Hoon's eyes has changed.

27
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:29,490
Jung Won, what should I do?

28
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:34,900
Father cherishes you
and Mom the most.

29
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:38,170
Don't you think the password
has something to do with you two?

30
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,040
Like a birthday or something?

31
00:01:41,270 --> 00:01:44,610
- You think he'd make it that easy?
- If not that,

32
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,680
then he must've written it down,
right?

33
00:01:48,180 --> 00:01:49,550
I'll look for it.

34
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:53,820
But what if I find the password?

35
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:55,790
What then?

36
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:59,020
You have to tell Se Hoon.

37
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,930
What?

38
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:02,590
Should I really do that?

39
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:04,930
We'll see what he does with it.

40
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:18,780
Hey, Jung Won.

41
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:23,210
What?
The password to the Swiss account?

42
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:28,420
It's not Dad's birthday.

43
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,060
Mom's birthday?

44
00:02:32,690 --> 00:02:33,690
(Incorrect PIN)

45
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:37,100
Or maybe my birthday?

46
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:39,530
(Incorrect PIN)

47
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,730
As if.

48
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:44,470
Maybe it's not four digits?

49
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:47,710
Don't tell me...

50
00:02:58,550 --> 00:02:59,850
(Folder, CEO Candidate, Overall
Management Direction for the Group)

51
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:00,920
(Next Board of Directors'
Meeting Agenda)

52
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,720
(Main Albums)

53
00:03:02,790 --> 00:03:04,960
(Camera)

54
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,690
If I were Dad,
where would I have hidden it?

55
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:12,930
(Calls)

56
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,230
(Recent Search:
Mr. Kim, Switzerland)

57
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:17,740
"Mr. Kim, Switzerland?"

58
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:21,370
He has contacts in Switzerland?

59
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:27,280
(Mr. Kim, Switzerland)

60
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,350
This doesn't look like
a phone number.

61
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:32,520
(Mr. Kim, Switzerland)

62
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:35,620
This is it.

63
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:54,170
(Mr. Kim, Switzerland)

64
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,220
It's 2.3 billion dollars.

65
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,720
It's 2.3 billion dollars.

66
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:14,490
I have the password
to Dad's Swiss account.

67
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:18,100
Now, Kunhyang is mine.

68
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,110
I got a text.

69
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,380
(Mr. Kim, Switzerland)

70
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:46,590
That's right.
It's 2.3 billion dollars.

71
00:04:47,090 --> 00:04:48,960
It's 2.3 billion dollars.

72
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:55,500
We need to change the password now.
Can you do it?

73
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:57,370
A window is popping up,
asking for a verification code.

74
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,970
Do we have to plant a spy app
on Jin Tae Seok's computer?

75
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,580
A spy app? Can we even do that?

76
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,480
It's possible
if we can buy ourselves some time.

77
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:08,280
Tell me what to do.

78
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,670
Care for a drink?

79
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,810
There's something
I'd like to discuss with you.

80
00:05:37,210 --> 00:05:38,210
A drink?

81
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,550
(Confirm Send?)

82
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:49,390
Sure.

83
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,500
(Economic Analysis: Past AI Hype,
Focus on Real Profit)

84
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,500
(Download Complete)

85
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,710
(Economic Analysis: Past AI Hype,
Focus on Real Profit)

86
00:06:14,610 --> 00:06:16,180
Okay, Jin Tae Seok.

87
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:17,720
He took the bait.

88
00:06:27,890 --> 00:06:29,990
- Hello?
- I changed the password.

89
00:06:31,660 --> 00:06:32,930
Okay, Ji Na.

90
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,270
Show me at the office tomorrow.

91
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,770
Was it Ahn Ji Na?

92
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:39,800
At this hour?

93
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:41,270
Yes.

94
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:45,980
Ji Na's just so ambitious.
She said she had a great idea.

95
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:54,090
That 2.3 billion dollars
must have been the source...

96
00:06:54,090 --> 00:06:55,290
of all your power.

97
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:57,590
What a shame.

98
00:06:57,590 --> 00:06:59,420
Now it's in my hands.

99
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:05,930
Oh my goodness! That's my Ha Neul!

100
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:10,700
- He's always so sweet.
- The 2.3 billion dollars is ours.

101
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:14,340
So what?
I'm not getting a single penny.

102
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:17,210
You think I just left it
sitting there?

103
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:20,880
You already moved it? Where to?

104
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:25,380
The Kunhyang Gallery's
slush fund account.

105
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,520
Isn't Cha Jung Won
in charge of the account?

106
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:30,150
Why? Don't you trust us?

107
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:33,620
How can I trust people?
I only trust money.

108
00:07:33,860 --> 00:07:36,730
No, just split it in half
and send it to my account.

109
00:07:36,890 --> 00:07:40,400
If you can't trust Jung Won or me,
then trust Ha Neul.

110
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:43,770
Chairman Joo Ha Neul
that you dote on so much.

111
00:07:44,370 --> 00:07:47,840
Of course I trust my Ha Neul.

112
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:51,540
By the way, Han Hye Ra,
what are you going to do now?

113
00:07:51,610 --> 00:07:55,750
- Are you just going to do nothing?
- I'm even busier...

114
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,650
than when I was chairman.

115
00:07:59,150 --> 00:08:00,150
(Madam Sa)

116
00:08:00,550 --> 00:08:01,550
Sa...

117
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:05,060
Yes, Madam Sa.

118
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:08,060
- Yes.
- Oh my.

119
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,590
Madam Sa?

120
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:14,800
Are they plotting behind my back?
This is suspicious.

121
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:17,570
Madam Sa...

122
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:23,410
Chairman Joo Ha Neul's regime
won't last long.

123
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,040
Their coalition is weak.

124
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:28,650
The board's majority has solidified
their support for Chairman Joo,

125
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:30,950
so we don't have enough grounds
to turn the tables.

126
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:32,980
And where do you think
we get our grounds?

127
00:08:33,450 --> 00:08:34,590
Have you forgotten?

128
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:38,660
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok's
slush fund.

129
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:40,790
It's in a Swiss account.

130
00:08:42,190 --> 00:08:45,630
Who do you think
manages that account?

131
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,100
I do.

132
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,900
It may be an off-the-books fund,

133
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:55,540
but if we control it,
the game is already won.

134
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,880
Let's turn the tables together.

135
00:08:58,280 --> 00:09:01,980
That slush fund carries a huge risk.

136
00:09:02,050 --> 00:09:05,450
For the directors who prefer
a legitimate flow of capital,

137
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,550
this could backfire...

138
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:09,790
Get your act together!

139
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:12,490
Is this any time to be quoting
a textbook on morals?

140
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:15,860
For project funds,

141
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:18,660
consolidating shares,
fending off legal risks...

142
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:22,300
Isn't it a piece of cake
to create plausible justifications?

143
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:24,800
What do you want from us?

144
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,170
I'm telling you
to pick the right side.

145
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:30,940
Before I completely upend the board.

146
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:38,920
Nice. This is totally my style.

147
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:43,320
You stepped down as chairman,
yet you seem to be glowing.

148
00:09:43,390 --> 00:09:45,620
It was just a passing title.

149
00:09:47,530 --> 00:09:49,730
I'm debating whether
to go back to my art,

150
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:53,400
or get more involved
with the gallery.

151
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:56,570
That's my point. Why did you
make your daughter the director?

152
00:09:57,800 --> 00:10:01,140
Why?
Is Jung Won not doing a good job?

153
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,840
Not at all. It's quite the opposite.

154
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:08,280
Is it because she's a designer?
Her academic record isn't special.

155
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:13,750
But her eye for art,
the way she presents gifts,

156
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:16,950
it's all so elegant and poised.

157
00:10:18,690 --> 00:10:19,820
Anything else?

158
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,630
And she's incredibly bold.

159
00:10:22,930 --> 00:10:25,500
Why? Did Jung Won do something rude?

160
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,570
But surprisingly, it works.

161
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:32,540
She'll give you a painting and say,
"Don't think of this as a gift."

162
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:33,940
- "The moment you accept this,"
- "The moment you accept this,"

163
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:36,710
"you incur a debt
you have to repay."

164
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:40,750
"Think carefully before you accept."
That's what I said, right?

165
00:10:40,850 --> 00:10:41,880
So audacious.

166
00:10:42,310 --> 00:10:43,810
Welcome, Director Cha.

167
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,820
You get prettier
every time I see you.

168
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:50,090
- You look more like your mother.
- Thank you for the compliment.

169
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,790
That makes me even happier.

170
00:10:55,190 --> 00:10:56,330
So, what's this about?

171
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,000
What do you want to discuss with me?

172
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:09,410
So the money from Honorary Chairman
Jin Tae Seok's Swiss account...

173
00:11:09,540 --> 00:11:11,080
is in the gallery's account now?

174
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:15,380
Only Chairman Gong, Chairman Joo,
and the three of us know.

175
00:11:15,450 --> 00:11:16,910
I'm the one managing it.

176
00:11:17,850 --> 00:11:19,650
Does Honorary Chairman
Jin Tae Seok know?

177
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:22,950
- Not yet.
- He'll find out soon enough.

178
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:25,060
This is going to be a war.

179
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:27,360
It was an embezzled slush fund
to begin with.

180
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:29,490
He can't exactly go public
with this.

181
00:11:30,090 --> 00:11:31,830
I'm shaking just thinking about it.

182
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:36,730
We need to move quietly...

183
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,740
with the Kunhyang Association
at the heart of it.

184
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:41,840
- How?
- we have to bring him down...

185
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:43,710
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok.

186
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:45,980
You want our Kunhyang Association
to do that?

187
00:11:57,250 --> 00:11:59,420
Madam Sa came to the gallery
to see Jung Won?

188
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,830
Yes, sir.

189
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:03,360
What are they conspiring about?

190
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:06,400
She was selecting gallery paintings
as gifts.

191
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:10,100
Hye Ra just stepped down
as chairman,

192
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:14,210
but she must be plotting something
behind my back.

193
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:32,360
So, you met with Madam Sa?

194
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:40,970
For the paintings we're giving
as gifts,

195
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:44,740
I chose works by Yoon Ji Woong
and Kim Sun Joo.

196
00:12:45,770 --> 00:12:46,770
And?

197
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:50,340
They're for Minister Kang Woo Jin
and Assemblyman Baek Seung Woo.

198
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:52,510
The paintings are currently valued
at ten thousand dollars,

199
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:55,710
We'll buy them back
for two million dollars in two years.

200
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:59,880
- Why are you telling me all this?
- Because in your eyes,

201
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,020
I saw the distrust.

202
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,390
You're just like Great King Yeongjo.

203
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:11,060
- Great King Yeongjo?
- He loved his son, but for power,

204
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:13,060
he killed his own child
without a second thought.

205
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:16,330
And until he passed the throne
to his grandson, Yi San,

206
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:19,400
he gambled with people's lives
countless times.

207
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:20,740
Just like you.

208
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:24,680
Isn't that a given?
We're talking about the throne.

209
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:28,980
You can't just give away such power,
even to your own child.

210
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:32,380
- The moment I let my guard down...
- They could poison you.

211
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,450
They're a mere possession...

212
00:13:34,890 --> 00:13:37,150
I created from my own bones,
flesh, and blood.

213
00:13:37,490 --> 00:13:39,090
How dare they think
of killing their own father?

214
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,730
So you're saying a father
can kill his own children, then.

215
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:43,190
Isn't that a given?

216
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:45,200
How dare you!

217
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:48,170
To gain power, and to keep it,

218
00:13:48,770 --> 00:13:50,600
you must become the Almighty.

219
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,500
Almighty?

220
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:56,810
An Almighty who can do
whatever you want...

221
00:13:56,810 --> 00:13:58,380
with your lover
and your own children?

222
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:05,050
I find myself saying things to you
that I could never say to Hye Ra.

223
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:08,550
That's because I'm the one
who's most like you.

224
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:11,020
Oh, right.

225
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:13,720
How's managing
the gallery's slush fund coming along?

226
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:18,500
- I'm handling it well.
- Good. I'm proud of you.

227
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:21,100
My Jung Won.

228
00:14:21,930 --> 00:14:24,170
Is there anything
you want to do with me?

229
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:26,040
I'd do anything for you.

230
00:14:30,470 --> 00:14:32,180
There is a place
I'd like to go with you,

231
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:35,150
but it might be difficult for you.

232
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:36,550
Where?

233
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:39,050
I'd go to the ends
of the earth for you.

234
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:54,830
Hey, you’re really not okay.
I need to get you to a hospital.

235
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:58,300
No, I can't. Not yet.

236
00:14:58,400 --> 00:15:01,870
"Not yet?"
You're not done being crazy?

237
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:03,510
You're the one
who's already lost it, Mom.

238
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:05,280
If you were in your right mind,

239
00:15:05,610 --> 00:15:07,880
how could you side with Han Hye Ra
over Se Hoon?

240
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:11,120
Why is everyone freaking out,
saying I've sided with Han Hye Ra?

241
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:15,250
You don't know how much I hate her.
This is just business.

242
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:18,960
My gut as the baddest woman says
to bet on Han Hye Ra now. That's it.

243
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:21,030
- You're wrong.
- About what?

244
00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:28,030
Se Hoon is about to kick Ha Neul out
and become the chairman.

245
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:30,430
He just got the most powerful weapon
in the world.

246
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,870
And what's that?

247
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:36,640
Don't tell me you two managed
to get Jin Tae Seok's slush fund.

248
00:15:36,710 --> 00:15:38,610
You know about the Swiss account?

249
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:42,350
How many times do I have to say it?
Your mother knows everything.

250
00:15:42,410 --> 00:15:44,680
I can see what's happening
for miles and miles.

251
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,580
You think that clairvoyance of yours
doesn't age?

252
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,620
Looks like your vision
is already going.

253
00:15:49,820 --> 00:15:53,320
Losing my vision, my foot!
I polish my crystal ball daily.

254
00:15:53,390 --> 00:15:54,760
But you're wrong this time.

255
00:15:55,730 --> 00:15:58,360
You'll regret it bitterly
if you mistreat Se Hoon.

256
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,200
Don't take my warning lightly.

257
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:03,330
Oh, dear.

258
00:16:04,130 --> 00:16:08,470
Jin Se Hoon has screwed up before,
so whatever.

259
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:13,040
But Young Chae has she gone mad?
Or is she just pretending to?

260
00:16:14,350 --> 00:16:16,810
Do you really think Jin Tae Seok
will show up there?

261
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:21,090
He will
if he really wants you on his side.

262
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:22,550
And if he doesn't?

263
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:24,820
Then,

264
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:27,690
that's Jin Tae Seok's true intentions
for now.

265
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:30,360
So tomorrow,
I'll know how much Jin Tae Seok...

266
00:16:30,730 --> 00:16:33,260
thinks I'm worth to him.

267
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,100
Exactly.

268
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,770
Are you quiet
because you're worried about me?

269
00:16:40,340 --> 00:16:41,340
Oh dear...

270
00:16:42,540 --> 00:16:45,710
You can read my mind
from my breathing. I'm impressed.

271
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:49,080
I don't need you to worry.
I need you to support me.

272
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:50,510
Okay?

273
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,120
I'm rooting for you.

274
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,720
And I have your back.

275
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,790
Of all places she could have chosen,
she wants me to go there.

276
00:17:05,100 --> 00:17:07,900
Right now,
I have no allies at Kunhyang.

277
00:17:08,470 --> 00:17:10,730
I have to get Cha Jung Won
completely on my side.

278
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,200
To use her as my sharpest...

279
00:17:14,870 --> 00:17:17,110
and most fatal blade.

280
00:17:30,250 --> 00:17:32,790
(Cha Ki Beom, Born: April 7, 1966,
Date of Death: November 28, 2025)

281
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:49,740
The whole world knows now...

282
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:52,640
that you were innocent, Dad.

283
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:56,380
And that Jin Tae Seok
killed Joo Sang Cheol.

284
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:59,920
(Cha Ki Beom, Born: April 7, 1966,
Date of Death: November 28, 2025)

285
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,520
So don't be in pain anymore.

286
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:05,090
Don't feel sorrowful...

287
00:18:05,690 --> 00:18:07,090
or wronged anymore.

288
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:12,860
Wherever you are,
play your guitar wholeheartedly...

289
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,830
and only cherish the good memories.

290
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:38,590
So, the place my Jung Won
wanted to visit with me...

291
00:18:40,390 --> 00:18:42,830
is Cha Ki Beom's tree burial site
of all places. Why?

292
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:44,390
You already know why.

293
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:48,400
You may be my biological father,

294
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:51,500
but from the day I was born
until this very moment,

295
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,700
the only father
engraved in my heart...

296
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:56,710
is the one resting here.

297
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,180
You brought me here
just to tell me that?

298
00:19:01,210 --> 00:19:02,810
I wonder...

299
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:05,280
what my late father would think...

300
00:19:06,050 --> 00:19:07,480
of this absurd twist of fate.

301
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:09,920
It doesn't get more ill-fated
than this.

302
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:12,420
My own biological father...

303
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:15,790
killed the father who raised me.

304
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:17,830
I had no choice.

305
00:19:23,430 --> 00:19:25,470
And you still want to accept me
as your daughter?

306
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:29,670
I'm trying to.

307
00:19:31,010 --> 00:19:33,010
As much as I hate to admit it,

308
00:19:34,580 --> 00:19:39,380
- you're far too much like me.
- Then for the man who raised me,

309
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:43,090
for my father, whom you killed,

310
00:19:43,850 --> 00:19:47,160
apologize right here in front of me.

311
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:49,660
What?

312
00:19:49,730 --> 00:19:52,400
You're not the only one
who gets to test me.

313
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:56,170
You need me, don't you, Father?

314
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:59,040
I also get to decide...

315
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:01,910
whether or not I can accept you...

316
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:05,310
- as my father.
- Unthinkable!

317
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:08,050
How dare you ask me, Jin Tae Seok,

318
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:11,320
to apologize to a worthless scumbag
like him!

319
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:18,990
Then the deal is off.

320
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:22,060
I guess you'll be all alone then...

321
00:20:23,430 --> 00:20:24,530
at Kunhyang.

322
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:27,860
Whether you and I...

323
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:30,670
are really related by blood or not,

324
00:20:31,970 --> 00:20:34,200
I'll have no choice but to drive a knife
through your heart.

325
00:20:36,540 --> 00:20:38,410
If I fail once,
I'll try a second time.

326
00:20:39,540 --> 00:20:41,450
If I fail again, I'll try ten times,

327
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:43,410
and 100 times.
Even 1,000 times if I have to.

328
00:20:55,090 --> 00:20:56,790
(Cha Ki Beom, Born: April 7, 1966,
Date of Death: November 28, 2025)

329
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:01,670
I'm sorry.

330
00:21:05,300 --> 00:21:09,270
I felt like
you stole Hye Ra from me.

331
00:21:11,210 --> 00:21:13,240
I hated you so much
I wanted you dead.

332
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:17,380
If I had known back then
that Jung Won was my daughter,

333
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:22,520
you never would have ended up
buried here.

334
00:21:26,890 --> 00:21:28,530
I sincerely apologize.

335
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:35,830
It doesn't matter
if you don't mean it.

336
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:39,740
You've admitted you were wrong
in front of my father.

337
00:21:42,770 --> 00:21:45,240
This act of apologizing...

338
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:47,710
and begging for forgiveness,
which you've never done before,

339
00:21:49,110 --> 00:21:52,180
is something you'll be doing
over and over, Jin Tae Seok.

340
00:21:54,250 --> 00:21:55,420
And slowly,

341
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:57,890
you will begin to crumble.

342
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:02,530
Miserably and all alone.

343
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,770
Jin Tae Seok...

344
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:16,470
apologized at Ki Beom's grave?

345
00:22:17,210 --> 00:22:18,840
And Jung Won made him do it?

346
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:30,890
- How is public opinion?
- There's been a clear shift.

347
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:34,360
Several of the boycott groups
have withdrawn their statements.

348
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:37,590
We're already getting calls
about contracts that were on hold.

349
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:39,830
I didn't expect a turnaround
this quickly.

350
00:22:40,330 --> 00:22:43,570
It means they trust the company,
not just the owner.

351
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,440
It was worth replacing
half of the board...

352
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:47,840
with outside directors
and even announcing a written pledge...

353
00:22:47,900 --> 00:22:49,040
to give up succession of management.

354
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:51,110
The stock is up,
but what about internal opposition?

355
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:53,610
How much longer
can we hold them off?

356
00:22:53,710 --> 00:22:55,510
That's all the more reason
we need to be transparent.

357
00:22:56,010 --> 00:22:58,120
Fair and objective rules
must come first.

358
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:03,790
Director Park,
once our credit rating stabilizes,

359
00:23:03,850 --> 00:23:06,490
I need you to revisit
the welfare projects we suspended.

360
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:07,960
Yes, Chairman.

361
00:23:08,290 --> 00:23:11,630
And proceed under the Kunhyang name,
not the owner's.

362
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:14,560
- Yes, I'll draft a proposal soon.
- The welfare projects?

363
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:17,200
Are you
prioritizing unprofitable work?

364
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,370
Vice Chairman Jin,

365
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:21,370
think of it as an investment
in reducing uncertainty.

366
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:25,580
It's the fastest way to show
Kunhyang isn't a private company.

367
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:29,310
Do you really not understand
why market sentiment is shifting?

368
00:23:29,850 --> 00:23:31,450
A major realignment
is urgently needed.

369
00:23:38,660 --> 00:23:42,960
Oh, dear. Jin Tae Seok
is acting out of character lately.

370
00:23:43,460 --> 00:23:45,900
It just goes to show how badly
he wants Jung Won's support.

371
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:49,400
I take it he still doesn't know
his account was emptied?

372
00:23:49,770 --> 00:23:54,640
Right. And Se Hoon still thinks
he controls the Swiss account.

373
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:58,010
At this rate, Cha Jung Won,
I mean, Jin Jung Won...

374
00:23:58,010 --> 00:24:00,610
is poised to be the successor
of Kunhyang.

375
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:03,880
There will be one final test.

376
00:24:03,980 --> 00:24:07,350
He's not one
to give up his power that easily.

377
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:10,690
Well, I wonder what
that final test could be.

378
00:24:10,890 --> 00:24:13,390
Jung Won might have to...

379
00:24:15,090 --> 00:24:16,830
risk her life again.

380
00:24:18,530 --> 00:24:21,830
"Those who seek death shall live,
and those who seek life shall die."

381
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:25,770
That was from Admiral Yi Sun Sin.
He's my favorite.

382
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:28,740
Do you think Jung Won
can pull it off?

383
00:24:28,810 --> 00:24:31,040
With my Ha Neul there
to back her up,

384
00:24:31,370 --> 00:24:32,910
it'd be weird if she couldn't.

385
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:38,050
Jin Tae Seok is dead meat.
Maybe getting stabbed in the back...

386
00:24:38,110 --> 00:24:41,220
by his own daughter will finally
knock some sense into him.

387
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:42,650
Times have changed.

388
00:24:43,950 --> 00:24:45,560
New wine into new wineskins.

389
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:48,390
That can only happen
once Jin Tae Seok is brought down.

390
00:24:53,530 --> 00:24:56,030
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

391
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:02,570
My poor baby. I can't imagine
how torn up she must be inside.

392
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:05,310
She thought he was her mortal enemy,

393
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,810
but he's her biological father...

394
00:25:08,410 --> 00:25:09,410
Mom.

395
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:12,780
You're here.

396
00:25:16,250 --> 00:25:17,250
Is it really true?

397
00:25:17,950 --> 00:25:19,920
Jin Tae Seok actually apologized?

398
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:21,420
He didn't mean it.

399
00:25:22,230 --> 00:25:24,590
He's not the kind of person
who would ever bow his head to anyone.

400
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:28,100
But he must listen to you,
since you're his daughter.

401
00:25:28,370 --> 00:25:30,330
Only because I'm useful
to him right now.

402
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:32,400
And that's what
makes it even creepier now.

403
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:36,510
I have to show him...

404
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:39,510
that he's not the only one...

405
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:41,850
who can do whatever he wants.

406
00:26:00,630 --> 00:26:02,530
Secretary Yoon!

407
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,400
You asked for me, sir?

408
00:26:08,270 --> 00:26:10,070
The password to my Swiss account
has been changed.

409
00:26:10,410 --> 00:26:12,880
How could anyone change a password
that only I know?

410
00:26:12,980 --> 00:26:16,380
It's impossible to change
without your personal info, sir.

411
00:26:16,450 --> 00:26:17,580
That's exactly my point.

412
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:22,290
It seems someone either accessed
your computer or hacked it.

413
00:26:23,420 --> 00:26:24,420
Hacked?

414
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:27,590
A few days ago, I saw Se Mi...

415
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:31,030
sneaking into your study, sir.

416
00:26:31,330 --> 00:26:32,330
Se Mi?

417
00:26:52,250 --> 00:26:53,980
That account I manage...

418
00:26:55,090 --> 00:26:56,620
I mean, the one in Switzerland.

419
00:26:58,690 --> 00:27:00,890
Did you figure out the password?

420
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:02,890
It was on my phone.

421
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:04,930
I understand why you're angry.

422
00:27:05,430 --> 00:27:09,270
But Se Hoon was so worried
about you.

423
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:11,430
He said he needed my help.

424
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:13,600
What? Se Hoon did?

425
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:20,210
Don't be scared.

426
00:27:20,810 --> 00:27:23,780
Just tell him the truth
that Se Hoon put you up to it.

427
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:30,490
I believed it was for you, Dad.

428
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:32,320
I'm sorry.

429
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:35,090
Se Hoon, how dare he...

430
00:27:46,770 --> 00:27:48,640
What? Why isn't this working?

431
00:27:57,410 --> 00:27:59,080
Did Father
already change the password?

432
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:04,590
- What do you think you're doing?
- You ungrateful brat.

433
00:28:05,060 --> 00:28:06,320
How dare you try to steal
my account?

434
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,320
And by tricking my daughter,
Se Mi, to do it?

435
00:28:08,430 --> 00:28:09,930
I had to at least
have that account...

436
00:28:10,460 --> 00:28:12,360
so you could finally see me
as your son.

437
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:14,960
- Isn't that right?
- A punk like you is my son?

438
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:19,500
In your dreams. You're worth
less than the dirt under my feet.

439
00:28:20,870 --> 00:28:22,770
I took in a pathetic worm like you,

440
00:28:23,170 --> 00:28:24,810
and you have the gall
to want to be my son?

441
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,480
Get out of my sight now.

442
00:28:28,380 --> 00:28:29,380
Father.

443
00:28:41,290 --> 00:28:44,260
(A Graceful Liar)

444
00:29:06,280 --> 00:29:07,980
I’ve never had a dad
like him either.

445
00:29:08,080 --> 00:29:09,750
He’s your father, so you
have to hold back your anger.

446
00:29:09,750 --> 00:29:10,750
Let's get out of here.

447
00:29:10,820 --> 00:29:12,090
I have to escape this misery.

448
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:14,520
So Jin Tae Seok said
that you were worth...

449
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:16,330
less than the dirt under his feet?

450
00:29:16,490 --> 00:29:20,600
If this can't break Jin Tae Seok,
then I'll have to find another way.

451
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:22,170
He's waiting to strike Jin Tae Seok.

452
00:29:22,170 --> 00:29:24,000
We can’t know
what Se Hoon will do next.

453
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:25,840
What's that vial?

454
00:29:26,140 --> 00:29:28,870
Jin Se Hoon is actually trying
to kill Jin Tae Seok.

455
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:31,040
Farewell, Jin Tae Seok.

456
00:29:33,810 --> 00:29:35,810
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
